metadata.name: Will Solana Make It?  #1
metadata.creator: Bankless
metadata.description:
Is Solana going to make it?
Price is down. Its major public backer, SBF, is out for the count…Will the network survive the bear market? 
We brought in the creator of Solana and the co-founder of Solana Labs Anatoly Yakovenko to ask exactly that. 
He shares the full Solana story, back to its earliest inflection points all the way to the current state of Solana today. 

This episode marks a pivotal point in Solana’s lifecycle at the depths of a bear market. 
Will Solana make it? It’s all or nothing now. 
Artwork generated from the timestamp [1:16:24 - 1:16:37] “My guess is that if you looked at all the product launches from inception of crypto to now, to what’s going to happen in the next 12-18 months, the next 12-18 months are probably going to be way more than everything else combined…”
